Introduction

Kim E-Z is a South Korean singer and actress. She initially debuted in Baby V.O.X as a leader and main rapper in charge of the sexy concept. After the group’s disbandment she went on to work as an actress as well as MC for Mnet.

In 2010 she married a non-celebrity, and they currently have 2 children together. E-Z has confirmed that she hasn’t retired, and would like to return to the entertainment industry once her children grow up.
